{
  "texts": [
    "Realistic financial accounting and robust reporting of failures are essential to accurately assess their value and safety in clinical settings.",
    "Broadly, there is an urgent need to develop a nationwide consensus and guidance for evaluating LLMs in healthcare, so that we may realize the tremendous promise these groundbreaking technologies have to offer.",
    "Author contributions: SB, YL, LOE, NHS conceived of the study, defined the main outcomes and measures.",
    "SB, LOE, YL searched the literature to identify the publications to review and categorized the publications.",
    "SB, LOE, YL and NHS drafted the manuscript."
  ]
}